This directory contains the subroutines for the tight-binding
"STATIC" program.  The online manual for this program is located
at http://cst-www.nrl.navy.mil/bind/static.  See
http://cst-www.nrl.navy.mil/bind for parameters.

See the file "REVISION_HISTORY" for information about changes in
this program since the previous release.

The file ALLSOURCE.tar.gz contains all of the source and parameter
(P1,P2,P3) files in this directory.

